{"id": "art-38", "label": "Art. 38", "title": "Art. 38: Competenţa curţii de apel", "slug": "art-38", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 38: Competen&#355;a cur&#355;ii de apel </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Curtea de apel judec&#259; în prim&#259; instan&#355;&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)infrac&#355;iunile\nprev&#259;zute de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul penal</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> la art. 394-397, 399-412 &#351;i 438-445;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)infrac&#355;iunile\nprivind securitatea na&#355;ional&#259; a României, prev&#259;zute în legi\nspeciale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_737824956\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2757\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_737824956\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>infrac&#355;iunile\ns&#259;vâr&#351;ite de judec&#259;torii de la judec&#259;torii, tribunale\n&#351;i de procurorii de la parchetele care func&#355;ioneaz&#259; pe\nlâng&#259; aceste instan&#355;e;</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) Prin Decizia nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>23/2022</span><span style='color:black'> Înalta Curte de\nCasa&#355;ie &#351;i Justi&#355;ie admite recursul în interesul legii &#351;i\nstabile&#351;te c&#259;, în interpretarea &#351;i aplicarea unitar&#259; a\ndispozi&#355;iilor art. 38 alin. (1) lit. c) &#351;i art. 40 alin. (1) din\nCodul de procedur&#259; penal&#259;, competen&#355;a instan&#355;ei de\njudecat&#259; în solu&#355;ionarea cauzelor penale având ca obiect\ninfrac&#355;iuni s&#259;vâr&#351;ite de judec&#259;tori &#351;i procurori care\nau dobândit un grad profesional superior celui al instan&#355;ei/parchetului în\ncare î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; efectiv activitatea se determin&#259;\nprin raportare la instan&#355;a/parchetul la care î&#351;i\ndesf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; efectiv activitatea magistratul cercetat, &#351;i nu\nla gradul profesional superior al acestuia.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1031202619\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2756\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1031202619\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)infrac&#355;iunile s&#259;vâr&#351;ite de avoca&#355;i,\nnotari publici, executori judec&#259;tore&#351;ti, de controlorii financiari ai\nCur&#355;ii de Conturi, precum &#351;i auditori publici externi;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1290352622\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2755\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1290352622\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)infrac&#355;iunile s&#259;vâr&#351;ite de &#351;efii\ncultelor religioase organizate în condi&#355;iile legii &#351;i de\nceilal&#355;i membri ai înaltului cler, care au cel pu&#355;in rangul de\narhiereu sau echivalent al acestuia;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1128513151\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2754\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1128513151\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)infrac&#355;iunile s&#259;vâr&#351;ite de\nmagistra&#355;ii-asisten&#355;i de la Înalta Curte de Casa&#355;ie &#351;i\nJusti&#355;ie;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_615723371\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2753\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_615723371\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)infrac&#355;iunile s&#259;vâr&#351;ite de membrii\nCur&#355;ii de Conturi, de pre&#351;edintele Consiliului Legislativ, de\nAvocatul Poporului, de adjunc&#355;ii Avocatului Poporului &#351;i de chestori;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1344905371\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2752\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1344905371\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)cererile de str&#259;mutare, în cazurile prev&#259;zute\nde lege.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Curtea de apel judec&#259;\napelurile împotriva hot&#259;rârilor penale pronun&#355;ate în prim&#259;\ninstan&#355;&#259; de judec&#259;torii &#351;i de tribunale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Curtea de apel\nsolu&#355;ioneaz&#259; conflictele de competen&#355;&#259; ivite între\ninstan&#355;ele din circumscrip&#355;ia sa, altele decât cele prev&#259;zute la\nart. 36 alin. (2), precum &#351;i contesta&#355;iile formulate împotriva\nhot&#259;rârilor pronun&#355;ate de tribunale în cazurile prev&#259;zute de\nlege.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Curtea de apel\nsolu&#355;ioneaz&#259; &#351;i alte cauze anume prev&#259;zute de lege.</span></p>"}